<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3389] Bnd iPOJO Plugin ignores annotated components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3389</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The bnd plugin uses the ${classes} Bnd macro to query the system for classes annotated with @Component or @Handler.&lt;br/&gt;
The query format in use was &quot;@Component|@Handler&quot; but it was not the expected Bnd format.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An appropriate Bnd annotation query should looks like &quot;org.apache.felix.ipojo.annotations.*&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
